description:
Tender Australian turkey breast delicately filled with dried cranberries, chestnuts and a delicious stuffing made with nutmeg, cinnamon & parsley.  
Slice and serve with a side of golden, roasted red onions, garlic & baby potatoes finished with a fresh rosemary garnish. 


Oven Heating Instructions: 
Heating times are a guide and may vary depending on your appliance. 

1. Preheat oven at 200°C (180°C Fan Forced). 
2. Remove joint from the plastic bag. 
3. Place product onto oven tray, spray one side of foil with oil and cover joint, oil side down. 
4. Place in the oven directly onto the middle rack and heat for 80 minutes. 
5. Remove foil from the joint and heat for a further 10 minutes until heated through. 
6. Remove joint from the oven and rest for 5-10 minutes. 
7. Carve and serve.
name: Woolworths Oven Roast Turkey Breast With Cranberry & Chestnut Stuffing 800g
